SP.P:
As for the men, the least said about them is the best;
and, as for their manners, egad! I never was treated with so much
ill-manners, by any other set of people, before or since!

Think no more of your false lover, Madam. Take my ad∣vice;
and, from among the noble youths of Florence, who lan∣guish for your
smiles, chuse one to whom I may resign you.
